Package: candid
Title: Candidate Annotation aNd Disease-informed Interpretation of eviDence
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Samuel", "Bharti", email = "sbharti@uab.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An agentic, R-native evidence-review workbench for research genomics.
    Turns a candidate list (variants, genes, or perturbation hits) plus a disease
    context into a plausibility-ranked, cited research review with caveats and
    suggested next experiments. Built on ellmer for provider-agnostic LLM
    orchestration and httr2 for public bio-database access. Research use only.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3)
